2. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper discusses potential security risks and limitations of the proposed system, as well as the societal impact of key replication technology. This suggests a focus on cryptography and security. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The use of deep neural networks for key detection and 3D model inference falls under the domain of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper describes the use of deep neural networks for key detection and 3D model inference, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper discusses the generation of 3D models of physical keys, which falls under the domain of computer graphics.
